title: Ceiling fans included, Spacious 9' ceilings, Stylish private cabanas

posting_body: ['Schedule a Tour Today: <URL>', 'Discover a life of ease at Palmetto Promenade.', 'At our luxury apartments in Boca Raton, residents will find a selection of one bedroom, two bedroom, and three bedroom homes that are sure to suit any lifestyle.', 'In each home, residents will enjoy the chef-caliber kitchens with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances, private balconies, and spacious closets with built-in shelving.', 'Throughout the community at our Boca apartments, residents can take advantage of the resort-style swimming pool with private cabanas, cutting-edge fitness center, and the outdoor entertainment area.', 'Amenities:', '-Dacora rocker switches and USB outlets in the living room and bedrooms', '-Modern one, two and three bedroom residences', '-Spa-inspired bathrooms with quartz vanities and', 'under mounted sinks, double vanity available in select residences', '-Amazing views of Boca Raton, the Boca Raton Country Club and beaches from upper level residences', '-Cutting edge fitness studio with cardio, strength training, Fitness On Demand and yoga studio', '-Wi-Fi access throughout residential amenities', '-Professional concierge services available', '-Porcelain tile tub and shower surrounds', '-Individually controlled heating and air conditioning with Nest thermostats', '-Whirlpool appliance package including French door with bottom freezer in stainless steel refrigerator', '-Custom closet built-ins available', '-Electric car charging stations', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
